hall Islands and Tonga). These data highlight how the financing landscape across the Asia-Pacific region is evolving. In aggregate, financing is growing and diversifying rapidly. This opens up opportunities to meet the scale of the sustainable development 50. Estimate given in Irish L, et al, 2009. Outsourcing Social Services to CSOs: Lessons from Abroad. See: http://documents.worldbank.org/curated/ en/517011468019451377/pdf/503850ESW0WHIT10Lessons0from0Abroad.pdf 51. Private development assistance: key facts and global estimates, Development Initiatives.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "cbe00c81-d40f-4f67-9067-c325ee636d02": {"__data__": {"id_": "cbe00c81-d40f-4f67-9067-c325ee636d02", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/achieving-sustainable-development-goals-progress-establishing-integrated-national-financing-frameworks-asia-pacific-region", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Achieving the Sustainable Development Goals - Progress on establishing integrated national financing frameworks in the Asia-Pacific region", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/achieving-sustainable-development-goals-progress-establishing-integrated-national-financing-frameworks-asia-pacific-region", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "24b5db0ddb6fcd6c7f9d114d951e73136f3811428cfd9d665423c81c1dbe9443"}, "2": {"node_id": "c0385b7e-7575-43e4-983e-ea5afa4aa94d", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/a